These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
House: ranch-style, modern, townhouse, cottage
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, mechanic, project-manager, entrepreneur
1. the mechanic is on the left of the journalist##1
2. the ranch-style house is the entrepreneur##1
3. the project-manager is on the right of the journalist##1
4. the modern house is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
5. the cottage house is on the left of the journalist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| House          | cottage | townhouse | modern | ranch-style   |
| Job   | mechanic  | journalist     | project-manager   | entrepreneur |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, oliveros, tiparillo, alhambra
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, mirinda, fanta, water
1. the alhambra-smoker is the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the chaman-smoker is on the far right##1
3. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
4. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
5. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Cigar   | tiparillo | alhambra | oliveros | chaman    |
| Beverage   | fanta    | mirinda      | soy-milk | water |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: yellow, blue, white, mauve
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, scooter, bus, tram
1. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
2. the person who likes yellow is the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person driving the scooter is on the far right##1
4. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
5. the person who likes white is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Color         | yellow | mauve | white   | blue |
| Transport   | motorbike   | bus | tram | scooter         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, ambient, rock, hip-hop
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, peach, pomegranate, banana
1. the person eating peach is the fan of hip-hop##1
2. the fan of ambient is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
3. the fan of ambient is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
4. the fan of ambient is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
5. the person eating raspberry is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | ambient | d&b  | rock      |
| Food         | peach | banana   | pomegranate | raspberry |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, musical, mystery, time-travel
The people have 4 different jobs:  project-manager, police-officer, coach, security-guard
1. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
2. the coach is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the security-guard##1
4. the police-officer is on the right of the coach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | mystery | musical | animation |
| Job    | project-manager       | security-guard | coach | police-officer     |

