.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, december, may, november
There 4 different types of food: corn, pear, eggplant, banana
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far right##1
2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
3. the person eating banana is on the left of the person eating pear##1
4. the person eating corn is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
5. the person eating banana is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Birthday   | november | may | january | december |
| Food           | corn      | eggplant | banana | pear    |

