2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far right##1
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left##1
4. the designer is on the far right##1
5. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the coach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Birthday   | june | february | january | march  |
| Job           | security-guard | project-manager | coach       | designer |

