.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
House: tower, art-deco, gothic-revival, victorian
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, march, june, december
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the art-deco house##1
2. the person who's birthday is in december is the victorian house##1
3. the art-deco house is on the right of the tower house##1
4. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| House         | gothic-revival | tower      | art-deco | victorian |
| Birthday   | april          | march | june     | december    |

