.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-9::.
City: san-francisco, colone, venice, boston
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, green, blood-red, coral
1. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
3. the person traveling to boston is on the far right##1
4. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
5. the person who likes coral is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |   3    |    4     |
| City   | colone    | venice       | san-francisco | boston   |
| Color     | green | blood-red | coral   | apricot |

