2. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
3. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person playing domino##1
4. the person playing snooker is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Cigar    | blend | montecristo  | dannemann | aristoff |
| Game   | billiard | domino | snooker          | go    |

