.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-11::.
House: ranch-style, colonial, cottage, victorian
There are 4 different favourite colors: mauve, blood-red, white, grey
1. the person who likes white is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
2. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person who likes white##1
3. the victorian house is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
4. the cottage house is on the far left##1
5. the colonial house is the person who likes white##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| House      | cottage | colonial  | ranch-style | victorian |
| Color   | mauve  | white | grey           | blood-red   |

