3. the photographer is on the left of the firefighter##1
4. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
5. the photographer is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Flower   | orchid | poppy | begonia | daisy  |
