2. the fan of folk is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1
3. the person eating avocado is the fan of salsa##1
4. the person eating avocado is on the left of the fan of folk##1
5. the person eating apple is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |   2    |   3    |    4    |
| Food   | avocado | strawberry  | zucchini | apple   |
| Music-Genre        | salsa | folk | metal    | funk |

