.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-16::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, motorbike, ship
There are 4 different nationalities: russian, japanese, brazilian, indonesian
1. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the car##1
2. the person driving the bike is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the bike is on the left of the brazilian##1
4. the russian is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
5. the person driving the car is on the left of the indonesian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4        |
| Transport           | bike | ship    | car    | motorbike |
| Nationality   | japanese      | brazilian | russian | indonesian       |

