.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, iced-tea, fanta, coffee
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, peas, lettuce, pear
1. the person eating pear is the person drinking fanta##1
2. the person drinking sprite is the person eating peas##1
3. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
5. the person eating pear is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |    3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | iced-tea      | fanta | coffee | sprite |
| Food     | cabbage | pear    | lettuce  | peas |

