.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-18::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, april, march, december
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, water-polo, parkour, cricket
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Birthday      | february   | december | april   | march      |
| Sport   | badminton | cricket      | water-polo | parkour |

