.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-19::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: amber, fuchsia, white, lavender
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, fish, hedgehog, cat
1. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
2. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is the person who likes white##1
4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
5. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person who likes amber##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |      3      |    4    |
| Color         | fuchsia | white | lavender | amber |
| Pet   | cat     | hedgehog    | goldfish      | fish   |

