.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
4 different games are played: whist, canasta, billiard, backgammon
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, lavender, apricot, green
1. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
2. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
3. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
4. the person playing backgammon is the person who likes green##1
5. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Game   | whist | billiard | canasta | backgammon   |
| Color     | apricot  | blood-red    | lavender       | green |

 